TI  - Nitrogen recovery in planted seedlings, competing vegetation, and soil in response to fertilization on a boreal mine reclamation site
T2  - Forest Ecology and Management
JO  - Forest Ecology and Management
VL  - 360
SP  - 60
EP  - 68
SN  - 03781127
DO  - 10.1016/j.foreco.2015.10.024
