TI  - Experimental reintroduction of the crayfish species Orconectes virilis into formerly acidified Lake 302S (Experimental Lakes Area, Canada)This paper is part of the series “Forty Years of Aquatic Research at the Experimental Lakes Area”.
T2  - Canadian Journal of Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences
JO  - Can. J. Fish. Aquat. Sci.
