TI  - Comparison of two plant functional approaches to evaluate natural restoration along an old‐field – deciduous forest chronosequence
T2  - Journal of Vegetation Science
JO  - J Vegetation Science
VL  - 20
IS  - 2
SP  - 185
EP  - 198
SN  - 1100-9233, 1654-1103
