TI  - A Comparison of Lake Trout Spawning, Fry Emergence, and Habitat Use in Lakes Michigan, Huron, and Champlain
T2  - Journal of Great Lakes Research
JO  - Journal of Great Lakes Research
VL  - 31
IS  - 4
SP  - 492
EP  - 508
