TI  - Concurrent Management of an Exotic Species and Initial Restoration Efforts in Forests
T2  - Restoration Ecology
JO  - Restoration Ecology
VL  - 13
IS  - 4
SP  - 584
EP  - 593
SN  - 1061-2971, 1526-100X
