TI  - Assessing Simple Versus Complex Restoration Strategies for Industrially Disturbed Forests
T2  - Restoration Ecology
JO  - Restoration Ecology
VL  - 13
IS  - 4
SP  - 639
EP  - 650
SN  - 1061-2971, 1526-100X
